OL,5, A whistleblower claims call handlers   
OL,6, working on behalf of Scottish Power are
OL,7, told to threaten customers with debt   
OL,8, enforcement - even over mistaken bills.
OL,10,FThe man, an employee of an outsourced  
OL,11,Fcompany, works in a call centre in the 
OL,12,Fwest of Scotland dealing with people   
OL,13,Fwho call to query outstanding balances.
OL,15,FHe said colleagues had also raised     
OL,16,Fconcerns over aggressive tactics.      
